                {
                    "class": "DepictionHeaderView",
                    "title": "Features",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": false
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSpacerView",
                    "spacing": 8
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
                    "title": "Prevent Termination",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": false
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "Prevents iOS from killing the selected apps, even under memory pressure. When backgrounded, the app is instantly deep-frozen with no CPU activity, preserving its exact last state. This keeps the app instantly resumable but increases RAM usage. Battery Impact: SMART BALANCE",
                    "useRawFormat": true
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSpacerView",
                    "spacing": 8
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
                    "title": "Prevent Suspension",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": false
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "Prevents iOS from ever suspending the selected apps. They will continue running full background cycles, receive notifications instantly, and complete tasks like uploads or GPS navigation - exactly as if they were still in the foreground. Battery Impact: HIGH",
                    "useRawFormat": true
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSpacerView",
                    "spacing": 8
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
                    "title": "Fast Freeze",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": false
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "Forces apps to freeze the moment they leave the foreground, skipping any background task grace periods (like finishing a network request). This stops all CPU and network activity immediately, saving more power than the default iOS behaviour. The app resumes from its frozen state without reloading. Battery Impact: EXCELLENT",
                    "useRawFormat": true
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSpacerView",
                    "spacing": 8
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
                    "title": "PREVENT TERM+FAST FREEZE",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": false
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "Combines both protections: apps cannot be killed by iOS, and they are instantly deep-frozen the moment they leave the foreground. Battery Impact: SMART BALANCE",
                    "useRawFormat": true
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSpacerView",
                    "spacing": 16
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionHeaderView",
                    "title": "Known Issues",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": false
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSpacerView",
                    "spacing": 8
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
                    "title": "WhatsApp",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": false
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "WhatsApp works perfectly with Fast Freeze and Prevent Suspension. It behaves strangely when targeted with Prevent Termination, so it has been bypassed for this category only. It functions normally with all other categories.",
                    "useRawFormat": true
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSpacerView",
                    "spacing": 8
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
                    "title": "Facebook",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": false
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "When targeting Facebook with Prevent Termination for the first time, you must reset app data or reinstall the app, otherwise a black screen appears. This issue is also present with Watchdog Pro and only affects the latest versions of Facebook. It does not occur on Facebook v560 and below.",
                    "useRawFormat": true
                },
